.Va next_in ,
.Va avail_in ,
.Va zalloc ,
.Va zfree ,
and
.Va opaque
must be initialized before by the caller.
.Pp
The
.Fa windowBits
parameter is the base two logarithm of the maximum window size
.Pq the size of the history buffer .
